    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi10">（一）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
都の花に魁けて<lb />
春足日をけふこゝに<lb />
明粧成りし水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi20">（二）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
明治の帝行幸して<lb />
叡覧ありしあとゞころ<lb />
由緒も深き水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi30">（三）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
大魚小魚鰭の数<lb />
集めてこゝに海の幸<lb />
綾うるはしき水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi40">（四）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
造りなしたる海の宮<lb />
竜宮城もよそならず<lb />
雅び床しの水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi50">（五）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
水際にあそぶ魚類の<lb />
ゆきゝ妙なる舞の袖<lb />
眺め見飽かぬ水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em"><seg rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi60">（六）</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
けふしも和む春の色<lb />
げに長閑なる茅渟の浦<lb />
いざ来て見ませ水族館<lb />
東洋一の水族館<lb />
堺水族館は開かれぬ<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
